name: MIS National incorrect ORA v3(2)
description:
This summary report returns counts by establishment of the prison population and how many of those do not have a nationality recorded in Prison-NOMIS. Prisoners admitted in the last 5 days are excluded.
PND0005 - v00.00.01 Last Modified: 05/09/12

dataset.name: Main Data
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT CASE WHEN AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS.LIFE_SENTENCE_FLAG = 'Y' THEN 'Life' ELSE TO_CHAR(AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS.YEARS) END AS CASE_TERMS_YEARS, CASE WHEN AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS.LIFE_SENTENCE_FLAG = 'Y' THEN '' ELSE TO_CHAR(AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS.MONTHS) END AS CASE_TERMS_MONTHS, CASE WHEN AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS.LIFE_SENTENCE_FLAG = 'Y' THEN '' ELSE TO_CHAR(AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS.WEEKS) END AS CASE_TERMS_WEEKS, CASE WHEN AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS.LIFE_SENTENCE_FLAG = 'Y' THEN '' ELSE TO_CHAR(AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS.DAYS) END AS CASE_TERMS_DAYS, AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY FROM BODIMIS.DIM_DATE AT_OFFENCE_DATE, BODIMIS.FACT_COURT_CHARGE AT_FACT_COURT_CHARGE, BODIMIS.FACT_SENTENCE_CHARGE AT_FACT_SENTENCE_CHARGE, BODIMIS.FACT_CASE_SENTENCE AT_FACT_SENTENCE, BODIMIS.DIM_ESTABLISHMENT AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP, BODIMIS.DIM_SENTENCE_TYPE AT_DIM_SENTENCE_TYPE2, BODIMIS.FACT_CASE_SENTENCE_TERM AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS, BODIMIS.DIM_SENTENCE_STATUS AT_DIM_SENTENCE_STATUS, BODIMIS.DIM_OFFENDER_BOOKING AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING, BODIMIS.DIM_COURT_CASE AT_COURT_CASE WHERE (AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS.SENTENCE_TYPE_SK = AT_DIM_SENTENCE_TYPE2.SENTENCE_TYPE_SK (+)) AND (AT_FACT_COURT_CHARGE.OFFENCE_DATE_SK = AT_OFFENCE_DATE.DATE_SK (+)) AND (AT_COURT_CASE.COURT_CASE_SK = AT_FACT_COURT_CHARGE.COURT_CASE_SK (+)) AND (AT_FACT_SENTENCE.SENTENCE_STATUS_SK = AT_DIM_SENTENCE_STATUS.SENTENCE_STATUS_SK (+)) AND (AT_FACT_COURT_CHARGE.OFFENDER_CHARGE_ID_NK = AT_FACT_SENTENCE_CHARGE.OFFENDER_CHARGE_ID_NK (+)) AND (AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK (+) = AT_FACT_SENTENCE_CHARGE.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK AND AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS.SENTENCE_SEQ_NK (+) = AT_FACT_SENTENCE_CHARGE.SENTENCE_SEQ_NK) AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK = AT_COURT_CASE.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK (+)) AND (AT_COURT_CASE.COURT_CASE_SK = AT_FACT_SENTENCE.COURT_CASE_SK (+)) AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK IN (SELECT CSL.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK FROM BODIMIS.DIM_STAFF_ACCESSIBLE_CASELOAD SAC, BODIMIS.DIM_CASELOAD_SECURITY_LIST CSL WHERE SAC.CASELOAD_ID = CSL.CASELOAD_CODE AND SAC.USERNAME = UPPER('DPRWS') AND CSL.ENDYEAR >= TO_CHAR(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 'YYYY') - 6)) AND (AT_COURT_CASE.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK IS NULL OR AT_COURT_CASE.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK IN (SELECT CSL.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK FROM BODIMIS.DIM_STAFF_ACCESSIBLE_CASELOAD SAC, BODIMIS.DIM_CASELOAD_SECURITY_LIST CSL WHERE SAC.CASELOAD_ID = CSL.CASELOAD_CODE AND SAC.USERNAME = UPPER('DPRWS') AND CSL.ENDYEAR >= TO_CHAR(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 'YYYY') - 6)) AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.ESTABLISHMENT_SK = AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ESTABLISHMENT_SK) AND (AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ACTIVE_FLAG = 'Y') AND ((AT_DIM_SENTENCE_TYPE2.SENTENCE_CODE_NK IN ('ADIMP_ORA', 'CUR_ORA', 'DTO_ORA', 'FTR_ORA', 'FTR_HDC_ORA', 'FTRSCH15_ORA', 'HDR_ORA', 'LR_ORA', 'SEC91_03_ORA', 'YOI_ORA', 'BOTUS', '14FTR_ORA', 'LR_YOI_ORA', 'LR_SEC91_ORA', '14FTRHDC_ORA')) AND CASE WHEN AT_OFFENCE_DATE.DAY_DATE < '31/12/9000' THEN AT_OFFENCE_DATE.DAY_DATE END >= TO_DATE('01-02-2015 00:00:00', 'DD-MM-YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.ACTIVE_FLAG = 'Y') AND AT_DIM_SENTENCE_STATUS.SENTENCE_STATUS = 'Active' AND AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK IN ((SELECT establishment_code FROM prompt_)))), dataset_ AS (SELECT CASE_TERMS_YEARS, CASE_TERMS_MONTHS, CASE_TERMS_WEEKS, CASE_TERMS_DAYS, ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK, OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, NaN || TO_NUMBER(CASE_TERMS_MONTHS) || NaN || NaN AS V_LENGTH_MONTHS_, TO_NUMBER(CASE_TERMS_YEARS) AS V_YEARS, TO_NUMBER(CASE_TERMS_MONTHS) AS V_MONTHS, TO_NUMBER(CASE_TERMS_WEEKS) AS V_WEEKS, TO_NUMBER(CASE_TERMS_DAYS) AS V_DAYS FROM dataset_base_)

dataset.name: Last ETL Refresh
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG.BUSINESS_DATE FROM BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG WHERE (BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG.LOAD_ID = (SELECT MAX(LOAD_ID) FROM BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG WHERE NOT LOAD_END_DATETIME IS NULL))), dataset_ AS (SELECT BUSINESS_DATE FROM dataset_base_)

dataset.name: Population
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT AT_PND_PRISONER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY) AS PRISON_POPULATION, DT_PND_CURRENT_EST.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK, DT_PND_CURRENT_EST.ESTABLISHMENT_DESCRIPTION FROM BODIMIS.DIM_OFFENDER_BOOKING AT_PND_PRISONER_BOOKING, BODIMIS.DIM_ESTABLISHMENT DT_PND_CURRENT_EST WHERE (AT_PND_PRISONER_BOOKING.ESTABLISHMENT_SK = DT_PND_CURRENT_EST.ESTABLISHMENT_SK) AND (DT_PND_CURRENT_EST.ACTIVE_FLAG = 'Y') AND (AT_PND_PRISONER_BOOKING.MIS_CURRENT_RECORD_IND = 'Y') AND (DT_PND_CURRENT_EST.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK IN (SELECT SAC.CASELOAD_ID FROM BODIMIS.DIM_STAFF_ACCESSIBLE_CASELOAD SAC WHERE SAC.USERNAME = UPPER('DPRWS'))) AND (AT_PND_PRISONER_BOOKING.ACTIVE_STATUS IN ('Active In', 'Active Out')) AND (AT_PND_PRISONER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK IN (SELECT CSL.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK FROM BODIMIS.DIM_STAFF_ACCESSIBLE_CASELOAD SAC, BODIMIS.DIM_CASELOAD_SECURITY_LIST CSL WHERE SAC.CASELOAD_ID = CSL.CASELOAD_CODE AND SAC.USERNAME = UPPER('DPRWS') AND CSL.ENDYEAR >= TO_CHAR(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 'YYYY') - 6)) AND (AT_PND_PRISONER_BOOKING.BOOKING_STATUS = 'O') AND (DT_PND_CURRENT_EST.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK <> 'ZZGHI') GROUP BY DT_PND_CURRENT_EST.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK, DT_PND_CURRENT_EST.ESTABLISHMENT_DESCRIPTION), dataset_ AS (SELECT PRISON_POPULATION, ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK, ESTABLISHMENT_DESCRIPTION FROM dataset_base_)

dataset.name: Main Data (1)
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, CASE WHEN AT_OFFENCE_DATE.DAY_DATE < '31/12/9000' THEN AT_OFFENCE_DATE.DAY_DATE END AS DATE_OF_OFFENCE FROM BODIMIS.DIM_DATE AT_OFFENCE_DATE, BODIMIS.FACT_COURT_CHARGE AT_FACT_COURT_CHARGE, BODIMIS.FACT_SENTENCE_CHARGE AT_FACT_SENTENCE_CHARGE, BODIMIS.FACT_CASE_SENTENCE AT_FACT_SENTENCE, BODIMIS.DIM_ESTABLISHMENT AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP, BODIMIS.DIM_SENTENCE_TYPE AT_DIM_SENTENCE_TYPE2, BODIMIS.FACT_CASE_SENTENCE_TERM AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS, BODIMIS.DIM_SENTENCE_STATUS AT_DIM_SENTENCE_STATUS, BODIMIS.DIM_OFFENDER_BOOKING AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING, BODIMIS.DIM_COURT_CASE AT_COURT_CASE WHERE (AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS.SENTENCE_TYPE_SK = AT_DIM_SENTENCE_TYPE2.SENTENCE_TYPE_SK (+)) AND (AT_FACT_COURT_CHARGE.OFFENCE_DATE_SK = AT_OFFENCE_DATE.DATE_SK (+)) AND (AT_COURT_CASE.COURT_CASE_SK = AT_FACT_COURT_CHARGE.COURT_CASE_SK (+)) AND (AT_FACT_SENTENCE.SENTENCE_STATUS_SK = AT_DIM_SENTENCE_STATUS.SENTENCE_STATUS_SK (+)) AND (AT_FACT_COURT_CHARGE.OFFENDER_CHARGE_ID_NK = AT_FACT_SENTENCE_CHARGE.OFFENDER_CHARGE_ID_NK (+)) AND (AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK (+) = AT_FACT_SENTENCE_CHARGE.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK AND AT_FACT_SENTENCE_TERMS.SENTENCE_SEQ_NK (+) = AT_FACT_SENTENCE_CHARGE.SENTENCE_SEQ_NK) AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK = AT_COURT_CASE.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK (+)) AND (AT_COURT_CASE.COURT_CASE_SK = AT_FACT_SENTENCE.COURT_CASE_SK (+)) AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK IN (SELECT CSL.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK FROM BODIMIS.DIM_STAFF_ACCESSIBLE_CASELOAD SAC, BODIMIS.DIM_CASELOAD_SECURITY_LIST CSL WHERE SAC.CASELOAD_ID = CSL.CASELOAD_CODE AND SAC.USERNAME = UPPER('DPRWS') AND CSL.ENDYEAR >= TO_CHAR(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 'YYYY') - 6)) AND (AT_COURT_CASE.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK IS NULL OR AT_COURT_CASE.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK IN (SELECT CSL.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK FROM BODIMIS.DIM_STAFF_ACCESSIBLE_CASELOAD SAC, BODIMIS.DIM_CASELOAD_SECURITY_LIST CSL WHERE SAC.CASELOAD_ID = CSL.CASELOAD_CODE AND SAC.USERNAME = UPPER('DPRWS') AND CSL.ENDYEAR >= TO_CHAR(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 'YYYY') - 6)) AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.ESTABLISHMENT_SK = AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ESTABLISHMENT_SK) AND (AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ACTIVE_FLAG = 'Y') AND ((AT_DIM_SENTENCE_TYPE2.SENTENCE_CODE_NK IN ('ADIMP_ORA', 'CUR_ORA', 'DTO_ORA', 'FTR_ORA', 'FTR_HDC_ORA', 'FTRSCH15_ORA', 'HDR_ORA', 'LR_ORA', 'SEC91_03_ORA', 'YOI_ORA', 'BOTUS', '14FTR_ORA', 'LR_YOI_ORA', 'LR_SEC91_ORA', '14FTRHDC_ORA')) AND CASE WHEN AT_OFFENCE_DATE.DAY_DATE < '31/12/9000' THEN AT_OFFENCE_DATE.DAY_DATE END < TO_DATE('01-02-2015 00:00:00', 'DD-MM-YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.ACTIVE_FLAG = 'Y') AND AT_DIM_SENTENCE_STATUS.SENTENCE_STATUS = 'Active' AND AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK IN ((SELECT establishment_code FROM prompt_)))), dataset_ AS (SELECT ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK, OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, DATE_OF_OFFENCE FROM dataset_base_)

filter.name: prefilter_
filter.query: prefilter_ AS (SELECT * FROM dataset_ WHERE V_LESSTHAN24 IN ('N'))

field.name: $ref:V_LENGTH_MONTHS_
field.legacySql:
=(ToNumber([Case Terms - Years])*12)+
(ToNumber([Case Terms - Months]))+
(ToNumber([Case Terms - Weeks])/52)*12+
(ToNumber([Case Terms - Days])/365)*12
